PREAMBLE

This E-Commerce Backend Software is released under a DUAL-LICENSE model:
  • FREE TIER for non-commercial and educational use
  • PAID TIER for commercial use with royalty obligations

The license you are eligible for depends on your deployment context and
revenue generation, not your stated intentions.

