SECTION 2: MANDATORY ATTRIBUTION CONDITIONS

These conditions are BINDING for ALL users. Attribution requirements apply
whether you use Free or Commercial Tier. Violations trigger enforcement.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.1 SOURCE CODE ATTRIBUTION (EVERY FILE)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

EVERY source code file MUST retain the original copyright header at the top:

/*
 * E-Commerce Backend/Marketplace
 * Original Creator: Himanshu
 * GitHub: https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu
 * License: Dual-License (Community / Commercial) v2.0
 *
 * [Your additions and modifications below this line]
*/

MANDATORY:
  ✓ Header must be in EVERY file containing original code
  ✓ Cannot be removed, commented-out, or modified
  ✓ GitHub link must be active and correct
  ✓ Original author name must remain unchanged

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.2 DOCUMENTATION ATTRIBUTION (README & API DOCS)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Your README.md MUST include an Attribution section:

## Attribution

Built on E-Commerce Backend by [Himanshu](https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu)

Licensed under Dual-License (Community/Commercial License v2.0)
[View Full License](./LICENSE)

API DOCUMENTATION must include:

```json
{
  "powered_by": "E-Commerce Backend",
  "original_creator": "Himanshu",
  "license": "Dual-License v2.0",
  "repository": "https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu"
}
```

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.3 RUNTIME ATTRIBUTION (API & DEPLOYMENT)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

API Response Headers MUST include:

```
X-Powered-By: E-Commerce-Backend v2.0
X-License: Dual-License by Himanshu
X-Attribution: https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu
```

Error Responses MUST include (visible to admins):

```json
{
  "error": "...",
  "powered_by": "E-Commerce Backend",
  "attribution": "Built by Himanshu - Dual-License v2.0"
}
```

Admin Dashboard MUST display in footer:

"Admin System | Powered by E-Commerce Backend"

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.4 VENDOR/PARTNER DISCLOSURE
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you are a vendor, partner, or agency deploying this Backend for a client:

  ✓ MUST disclose to client that software is based on this backend
  ✓ Include link to repository in contract
  ✓ Mention license requirements in statement of work
  ✓ Include in technical documentation delivered to client

Failure to disclose = ₹50,000 penalty + license suspension

