───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
3.1 WHAT CONSTITUTES VIOLATION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

❌ COMMERCIAL USE WITHOUT LICENSE:
   • Any commercial deployment without paid Commercial License
   • Revenue generation (subscription, transaction fees, etc.)
   • Use by registered business entity

❌ BREACH OF ATTRIBUTION:
   • Removing copyright headers from source code
   • Removing attribution from documentation
   • Hiding/minimizing API header attribution
   • False claim of original authorship
   • Vendor failing to disclose to client

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
3.2 ENFORCEMENT & DAMAGES
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

DETECTION:
  • Automated API endpoint monitoring
  • GitHub repository scanning
  • Public instance discovery
  • Community reports

CURE PERIODS:
  • First violation: 7 days
  • Second violation: 3 days
  • Third+ violation: 0 days (immediate termination)

ENFORCEMENT ACTIONS (if not cured):
  ✗ License TERMINATED immediately
  ✗ DMCA takedown notices to hosting/domain providers
  ✗ Injunctive relief to cease operations
  ✗ Legal action & damage claims pursued

DAMAGES:
  💰 ₹30,000-₹1,00,000 per day of violation
  💰 ₹75,000 per removed header
  💰 ₹1,00,000-₹2,50,000 per hidden attribution instance
  💰 Retroactive royalties at 15% penalty rate
  💰 All legal and enforcement costs

